about:
Once apon a time, there was a Snake who played minecraft. 

Snake: 'What's minecraft?'
Notch: 'Minecraft is a game where players can build/design houses or even PvP!'
Snake: (yawn) 'sounds boring.'
Notch: 'Join Avic.us and I assure you you'll change your mind'
Snake: 'Screw this I'm going too narnia!'
(Opens wardrobe, finds AV)
